OL,6,F"I want to first again express my
OL,7,Fdeepest sympathy for all of those
OL,8,Faffected by the Omagh bombing in
OL,9,FAugust 1998," said Secretary of State
OL,10,FChris Heaton-Harris, as he set out the
OL,11,Fterms of reference in a written
OL,12,Fstatement to Parliament on Wednesday.
OL,14,F"It was a cruel atrocity carried out,
OL,15,Fnot just on the people of Omagh, but
OL,16,Fon all those in Northern Ireland who
OL,17,Fsupported the peace process.
