OL,6,F"Following the announcement of the
OL,7,FInquiry in February 2023, and the
OL,8,Fappointment of Lord Turnbull as Chair
OL,9,Fin June 2023, I have now agreed with
OL,10,FLord Turnbull the Terms of Reference
OL,11,Ffor the Inquiry.
OL,13,F"These are focused on the four grounds
OL,14,Fidentified by the Northern Ireland
OL,15,FHigh Court as giving rise to plausible
OL,16,Farguments that the bombing could have
OL,17,Fbeen prevented."
