OL,6,FMr Heaton-Harris ordered the
OL,7,Findependent inquiry into the atrocity
OL,8,Flast year, in response to a court
OL,9,Fjudgment that directed the government
OL,10,Fto establish some form of
OL,11,Finvestigation.
OL,13,FMichael Gallagher, whose son Aiden
OL,14,Fdied in the Real IRA bombing, took the
OL,15,Flegal challenge that resulted in the
OL,16,Fjudge directing the state to act.
