OL,6,FIt will also examine claims around
OL,7,Finformation allegedly passed to the
OL,8,Fsecurity forces by a state agent known
OL,9,Fas Kevin Fulton in the months prior to
OL,10,Fthe Omagh attack.
OL,12,FThe inquiry will also look at
OL,13,Fintelligence said to have been
OL,14,Fobtained by the UK Government's
OL,15,FCommunication Headquarters (GCHQ) from
OL,16,Falleged vehicle and telephone
OL,17,Fmonitoring of dissident republicans
OL,18,Finvolved in the planning, preparation
OL,19,Fand conduct of the Omagh bombing and
OL,20,Fother earlier attacks.
