OL,6,FThe subsequent analysis and handling
OL,7,Fof the GCHQ intelligence by the state
OL,8,Fauthorities will also be investigated.
OL,10,FThe inquiry will also examine the
OL,11,Fextent and adequacy of steps taken by
OL,12,FUK state authorities to track and
OL,13,Fanalyse the mobile telephone usage by
OL,14,Fthose suspected to be involved in
OL,15,Fdissident republican terror attacks
OL,16,Fbefore the Omagh bombing and whether
OL,17,Fthat data may have aided efforts to
OL,18,Fdisrupt the atrocity in Omagh.
