OL,6,FChris Heaton-Harris reiterated his
OL,7,Fcall for the Irish Government to set
OL,8,Fup its own inquiry into the Omagh
OL,9,Fbombing.
OL,11,FIn his 2021 judgment, Mr Justice
OL,12,FHorner directly recommended that the
OL,13,FUK Government carried out an
OL,14,Finvestigation into alleged security
OL,15,Ffailings in the lead-up to the 1998
OL,16,FReal IRA atrocity that killed 29
OL,17,Fpeople, including a woman pregnant
OL,18,Fwith twins.
