OL,7,FTurnbull said he was confident the
OL,8,Fterms of reference would allow him to
OL,9,Fconduct a "thorough and robust
OL,10,Finvestigation".
OL,12,F"The first thing to stress is that the
OL,13,Finquiry is an entirely independent
OL,14,Fbody," he said.
