OL,6,F"I and my team will decide which are
OL,7,Fthe relevant and important issues to
OL,8,Fexplore and which witnesses will be
OL,9,Fcalled. We will do so in a manner
OL,10,Fwhich is entirely free of influence
OL,11,Ffrom the Government, or any of the
OL,12,FUnited Kingdom authorities and
OL,13,Fagencies.
OL,15,F"The inquiry is established under the
OL,16,Fprovisions of the Inquiries Act of
OL,17,F2005 which means that I will have the
OL,18,Fpower to require the production of
OL,19,Fdocuments and the attendance of
OL,20,Fwitnesses. I shall make use of those
OL,21,Fpowers to any extent necessary."
