OL,6,FLord Turnbull said the voice of the
OL,7,Fvictims would be heard.
OL,9,F"Whilst I have not yet defined the
OL,10,Fexact procedure the inquiry will
OL,11,Ffollow, it is my intention to invite
OL,12,Ffamilies and survivors to
OL,13,Fcommemorative hearings in Omagh at
OL,14,Fsome point this year, so I can hear
OL,15,Fdirectly from those most affected by
OL,16,Fthe bombing," he said.
