OL,6,F"I recognise that for some, however,
OL,7,Frevisiting events of the past would be
OL,8,Ftoo traumatic and that they may have
OL,9,Fno wish to return to such a difficult
OL,10,Ftime in their lives and the lives of
OL,11,Ftheir own loved ones. I will fully
OL,12,Frespect that view, and the Inquiry
OL,13,Fwill recognise your privacy if this is
OL,14,Fyour wish."
OL,16,FThe first phase of the inquiry will
OL,17,Finvolve gathering information and
OL,18,Fmaterials.
