OL,7,Fevidential hearings and Lord Turnbull
OL,8,Fsaid he intended for those to be held
OL,9,Fin public and broadcast live, unless
OL,10,Fit was necessary in the public
OL,11,Finterest for reasons of national
OL,12,Fsecurity that they are held in private.
OL,14,FThe chairman acknowledged it could
